    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>
                <date>May 28<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1868</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Sir, Yours of the <date>1st of Apr.</date> just now to hand<lb/> in reply to
                    <sic>wich</sic> I have to state, that I have <del>only</del><lb/> subscribed to
                the Occident only since last year, and<lb/> consequently <sic>cannt</sic> owe to the
                Estate more than<lb/> for one year and two months. If you find that<lb/> correct,
                please let me know so, and I will remit by<lb/> next mail $4.75/100 in liquidation
                of my indebtedness to<lb/> the Est to date. Please stop anyhow sending the<lb/>
                Occident, as I <sic>cannt</sic> afford to keep it any longer</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <persName role="author">L Weiskopf</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="The following is written in pencil near the bottom left.">send bill as
                above<lb/> WBH.</p>
        </body>
    </text>
